cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.AI, cs.HC 

The paper deals with the application of machine learning algorithms on neuroimaging data for the detection of Autism Spectrum Disorder (ASD). This falls under the domain of computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.AI). Additionally, the study also involves the neuroscience domain, which could potentially fall under human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
